Newcastle Captain Kevin Nolan to Undergo Surgery on Right Ankle

-- B y   B o b   B e n s c h
-- 
2011-05-12T12:08:46Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-12/newcastle-captain-kevin-nolan-to-undergo-surgery-on-right-ankle.html
Newcastle captain  Kevin Nolan  will
have surgery on his right ankle today and miss the final two
games of the season, the Premier League club said on its
website.  Nolan has been troubled by an ankle problem all season and
today’s “minor” operation will allow him to be ready for the
start of preseason in July, Newcastle said.  Goalkeeper Steve Harper will also had a planned operation
on his left knee tomorrow in order to be ready for the
preseason, the club said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Bob Bensch at 
 bbensch@bloomberg.net  